	â€¢	Transformation â†’ toUpperCase, toLowerCase, trim, padStart, padEnd, repeat
	â€¢	Extracting â†’ slice, substring, substr
	â€¢	Splitting â†’ split, (join via Array)
	â€¢	Regex â†’ match, replace, search